The paper focuses on developing an annotation tool for LiDAR point clouds, which is a key component for autonomous vehicles. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also proposes the use of deep learning algorithms for LiDAR-based detection, which falls under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper discusses the challenges of annotating LiDAR point cloud data, which could also be relevant to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) category.
